306
00:20:18,040 --> 00:20:19,110
That's good.

307
00:20:20,800 --> 00:20:22,310
You told me that

308
00:20:22,920 --> 00:20:25,400
my son asked you to be here

309
00:20:25,400 --> 00:20:27,190
from far away to

310
00:20:27,710 --> 00:20:30,400
