325
00:21:16,350 --> 00:21:16,950
You just tell me

326
00:21:16,950 --> 00:21:18,040
where the kitchen is.

327
00:21:19,000 --> 00:21:20,230
It's over there.

328
00:21:21,280 --> 00:21:22,280
Mr. Fei.

329
00:21:23,520 --> 00:21:24,560
