343
00:22:01,230 --> 00:22:02,430
Practice medicine?

344
00:22:04,070 --> 00:22:06,160
If he is driven out of the family,

345
00:22:06,160 --> 00:22:07,190
he could be a doctor to

346
00:22:07,190 --> 00:22:08,920
