477
00:29:09,950 --> 00:29:11,830
If only you have a good judgement,

478
00:29:11,950 --> 00:29:13,800
response, speed

479
00:29:14,000 --> 00:29:14,880
and power,

480
00:29:18,230 --> 00:29:19,470
