505
00:32:09,680 --> 00:32:10,830
Teacher, you are too...

506
00:32:11,230 --> 00:32:12,310
Teacher.

507
00:32:13,520 --> 00:32:14,710
You went too far.

508
00:32:14,710 --> 00:32:15,710
Why didn't you say you went too far

509
00:32:15,710 --> 00:32:17,070
