514
00:32:39,000 --> 00:32:41,110
It's my turn to teach him today.

515
00:32:43,070 --> 00:32:44,680
Let me teach him today.

516
00:33:16,350 --> 00:33:17,070
Uncle.

517
00:33:17,350 --> 00:33:19,230
