543
00:35:03,840 --> 00:35:05,080
How did you make it?

544
00:35:05,840 --> 00:35:09,320
The inner part is toxic but the skin is not.

545
00:35:10,230 --> 00:35:12,630
Just think about it.

546
00:35:30,320 --> 00:35:31,520
Gotcha!

547
00:35:32,280 --> 00:35:33,120
What poison is it?

548
00:35:34,000 --> 00:35:36,670
